node.text: You have to go to @mendeecees to see the full video. Tell him do more! I told him i wanted to teach him this new TikTok dance to help me introduce the new Men’s Line. When I say i was dying laughing on the inside😂😂😂😂😂. He let me film a “practice” video in his phone. It was for my pure enjoyment and laughter. Never though he would post it. I promise you this man is FUNNY but you’d never know because he’s so reserve in public. But OMG he cracks me up. We had a stupid argument right before this so he felt bad and wanted to be supportive. I was trying to see how far I could push him past his comfort zone. (Somehow I deleted this off my page had to repost🤣🤣)

node.text: @GoddessDetox Vaginal Steaming has been seen as a way for women to reconnect with themselves, their wombs and vaginas. It is also a holistic alternative that has been known to help women reduce menstrual cramping, increase natural lubrication, increase libido and cleanse out excess matter in the womb. It is also a very powerful way to detox your ex’s energy from you and supercharge your womb for manifestation ✨🔮🧿 Follow @GoddessDetox and try their Queens Complete Vaginal Steaming Set  GoddessDetox.org

Can you believe this will be our 5th Pop Up in Atlanta! We appreciate all your support immensely! The next one will go down on Saturday, August 28th and will commemorate the End Of Summer! So don’t miss our last Pop Up of the Summer! 

To Register, send an intro of your brand/products pics and links to 
Rae@TheHolliday-Agency.com (please check the spelling). Registration correspondence will be completed in the order they are received. 
For Returnees, you know what to do! 

We are ending the Summer with a BANG! DJ,’s, Food Trucks, beautiful people, and of course, our VENDORS! 

Location: 
…..
Yelle Skin Care (Outside) 
55 Upper Alabama St Atlanta, GA 30303
Make sure you follow 👉🏾👉🏾👉🏾👉🏾 @TheBigBlackPopUp 🛍

.

node.text: Yes!!!! It’s official. I’m opening a restaurant!!!! But I’m learning…NO MORE SPENDING MY OWN MONEY!!!! I’ve learned credit is KING (or Queen). You don’t want to be staring opportunities in the face and you can’t move forward because you have made bad decisions with your credit. The good thing is it’s not too late to fix it. Hit up @mikethecreditchamp and he’ll get you right. Get negative items removed. Boost your credit score, clean up your past and get started on your future!

node.text: These two have been using it well before we released it to the public and said they wanted to be the faces of the brand. I told them they’d have to shoot videos. Notice all the personality when they think the cameras are just recording a “practice” shot. The minute they think it’s the real deal they get all shy and weird acting. I was cracking up inside! Overall I think they did a great job when they finally got it together. Show Marques and @lilmendc some love on their first @yelleskincare FRESH START VIDEO! If you’re a teen and you got what it takes to be a Face of Yelle Fresh Start, Get the system and tag me on your videos. I can’t wait to post them on my page!

.
 WE STILL HAVE A FEW SPOTS LEFT FOR THIS WEEKEND’S BIG BLACK POP UP SHOP!!! 
We appreciate all your support immensely! The next one will go down on Saturday, August 28th and will commemorate the End Of Summer! So don’t miss our last Pop Up of the Summer! 

To Register, send an intro of your brand/products pics and links to 
Rae@TheHolliday-Agency.com (please check the spelling). Registration correspondence will be completed in the order they are received. 
For Returnees, you know what to do! 

We are ending the Summer with a BANG! DJ,’s, Food Trucks, beautiful people, and of course, our VENDORS! 

Location: 
…..
Yelle Skin Care (Outside) 
55 Upper Alabama St Atlanta, GA 30303
Make sure you follow 👉🏾👉🏾👉🏾👉🏾 @TheBigBlackPopUp 🛍

node.text: You have to go to @mendeecees to see the full video. Tell him do more! I told him i wanted to teach him this new TikTok dance to help me introduce the new Men’s Line. When I say i was dying laughing on the inside😂😂😂😂😂. He let me film a “practice” video in his phone. It was for my pure enjoyment and laughter. Never though he would post it. I promise you this man is FUNNY but you’d never know because he’s so reserve in public. But OMG he cracks me up. We had a stupid argument right before this so he felt bad and wanted to be supportive. I was trying to see how far I could push him past his comfort zone. (Somehow I deleted this off my page had to repost🤣🤣)

node.text:
Y’all have no idea where this relationship started. Man we  were both young and trying to navigate this work, life, space. Now 10 years later we understand the game is to be told not sold! Posted @withregram • @courtneyadeleye #CASuiteRetreat is back!

The Super Suite Power Retreat!

Here’s your chance to enter into Courtney Adeleye’s world and experience it all! For 4 straight days step into Courtney’s life of self- pampering, relaxation, and enjoying the luxurious high life right down to learning her gridiron business techniques, industry conquering secrets, successful bawse to bawse networking and so much more! Get the chance to pick Courtney’s mind and see what exactly makes her tick, what drives her, and what motivates her. This retreat will not only be power-packed with opulence and leisure, but will also give you an eye-opening, enlightening and resourceful experience that you will mentally build on for years to come.

A Peek into The Super Suite Power Retreat itinerary:
Bawse to Bawse Power Networking
5-Star Cuisines prepared by Courtney’s own Private Gourmet Chef
A Disney VIP Experience
Courtney’s “Let’s Get Down To Business Bawse Meeting and Discussion”
Courtney’s Warehouse Tour
$500.00 Olbali Shopping Spree

PLEASE NOTE: While this setting will be very relaxed, we anticipate this event to include some high-level private BAW$E conversation with sensitive information to be shared by Courtney and other BAW$ES. For this reason, the Retreat will not be streamed online or audio recorded. Personal camera & video recording may be limited during certain activities.

www.CourtneyAdeleye.com
